Product name: Something Old, Something New, Something Borrowed, Something Blue Bridal Pin Keepsake
Description:
A personalized Bridal Charm Pin. This pin represents part of the traditional rhyme: Something Old, Something New, Something Borrowed and Something Blue.  The bridal pin can be attached to the inside of the wedding dress, on the bridal bouquet, bridal bag etc. 
Makes a Perfect gift for the Bride to Be. 
Bridal pin comes displayed in a gift box with a miniature card and keepsake blue bag for storage that reads Something Old, New, Borrowed Blue for the bride to be.
Old:  Photo frame charm,buyer can insert an old cherished photo inside the photo frame to accompany her down the aisle.
New: Brides new initials  (personalized letters A-Z)
Borrowed: Luck on special day, represented by good luck charm.
Blue: A heart shaped something blue charm with blue gem.
(Please provide initials, wedding date, in the Note section at Check Out.) 
If you want me to add a picture please screen shot picture with two faces maximum . If you would like a photo added for no additional charge please add it in the conversation section at checkout or after.
